T1  - Credit Lines and the Liquidity Insurance Channel
AU  - ACHARYA, VIRAL V.
AU  - ALMEIDA, HEITOR
AU  - IPPOLITO, FILIPPO
AU  - PEREZ-ORIVE, ANDER
